lead_paragraph: Thousands of grieving fans in green and white filled the Chapecoense stadium in remote southern Brazil on Tuesday, singing their team's praises and chanting one by one the names of players who lost their lives in a plane crash a day earlier.

headline.print_headline: Brazilian Town Grieves Loss of Cinderella Soccer Team
